nodes.title: Note about saved images
widgets_values: All generated images can be found inside your ComfyUI folder, in the output folder, organized into subfolders named by date in the format year-month-day

nodes.title: Setup
widgets_values:
Before the first run, expand the FluxMagic node and set the following:
- AE
- T5
- CLIP
- UNet Name

Other useful settings can also be configured in this node.

Logo Description:
A minimalistic, dark silhouette of Kikimora standing in the swamp. The figure is hunched, with ragged, tattered clothes blending into the background. Her form is sharp and angular, creating a haunting, shadowy presence. The outline should be bold and clean, evoking a sense of mystery and unease without excessive detail.

Kikimora:
Her glowing red eyes are the only distinct feature, piercing through the darkness. These eyes should be the focal point of the logo, glowing eerily within the shadowy form. The overall design should suggest an ancient, otherworldly figure, with a slight, haunting glow from the eyes providing contrast.

Atmosphere and Style:
The logo should maintain a minimalistic and monochrome style, using mostly black for the silhouette and dark tones. The background is simple and subtle, with perhaps a faint mist or abstract suggestion of the swamp environment, but without distracting from the silhouette itself. The design should communicate primal fear and mystery, with a focus on Kikimora’s unsettling, watching presence.

Prompt: Describe the image you want to generate.

Width and Height: Ignored if Aspect Ratio is not set to "Custom."

Aspect Ratio: Choose a preset ratio or select "Custom" to manually set dimensions.

Amount: Defines how many images to generate.

Press Ctrl + Enter or click Queue to start generating
